node port range:--
30000 to 32767

------------------------------

rollback command to previous version

kubectl rollback undo deployment (deployment name)



k8s trobuleshoot pods:-
to edit the pod:-
kubectl edit pod (podname)

way -----------
kubectl get pods (podname) -o yaml
------------


kubernets deployment roolback commands:-

kubectl rollout undo deployment (deploymentname)


how to pause deployment without affecting to deployment:--


kubectl rollout pause deployment (deploymentname)

how to resume deployment:-

kubectl rollout resume deployment (deploymentname)
